====Usage note====
even if it is translated as to [[be]], 是 is used only to link two nouns.
{{zh-usex|我 是 老师。|I am a teacher.}} {{zh-usex|我 是 中国人。|I am chinese.}}
It can't be used to link a noun and an adjective. The following sentence is wrong :
: 这是好。
The correct sentence is : 
{{zh-usex|这 很 好。|This is good.}}
Here [[很]] does not mean very. it is used to link a noun and an adjective.

